Classification.Comment: For these reasons, this variant has been classified as Pathogenic. This variant has not been reported in the literature in individuals affected with GBA2-related conditions. A gross deletion of the genomic region encompassing the full coding sequence of the GBA2 gene has been identified. Loss-of-function variants in GBA2 are known to be pathogenic (PMID: 23332916, 23332917). The boundaries of this event are unknown as they extend beyond the assayed region for this gene and therefore may encompass additional genes.
